        "Name": "Minsk 103 X",
        "Details": "The Minsk is Clan Ghost Bear's first domestically produced heavy BattleMech. Produced after Operation KLONDIKE's Arcadia campaign, the Minsk served the Ghost Bears in command and support Stars as a bodyguard unit. The design was retired for more than a century as Clan warriors disliked serving as a bodyguard, though the Bears resurrected it in the 3060s to bulk out their touman. An Active Probe provides minor e-war capabilities. This version has been updated by the Jade Falcons to mount a hyper gauss rifle, which gives the design heavier firepower.<br><br>X-class mechs feature upgrades to their armour, thermal management and defensive systems that improve their survivability on the 31st century battlefield.",
